snippet.title: Wonderland Adventures 2 Trailer
snippet.description: The official release trailer for Wonderland Adventures: Mysteries of Fire Island, the latest chapter in the best-selling and award-winning Wonderland series of puzzle adventure games. Play it now at www.midnightsynergy.com
